        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for revisions in 2d ed. of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Suggests correction regarding species numbers in the Tertiary.</p>  
<p>Comments on pages of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> and problems of German translation.</p> 
            <p>Believes CD’s theory not yet proven, but that it will finally lead to truth.</p>
        </abstract>
